<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Already Subscribed - Paper Street Thrift</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      background-color: #F8F3EA;
      color: #1B2B38;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(27, 43, 56, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5AACAA 0%, #4A9C9A 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    .info-icon {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .info-icon svg {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      fill: #5AACAA;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #1B2B38;
    }

    .message strong {
      color: #5AACAA;
    }

    .details {
      background: #F8F3EA;
      border-left: 4px solid #5AACAA;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .details p {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .details p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      background: #F8F3EA;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #1B2B38;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>You're Already Subscribed!</h1>
      <p>No action needed</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="info-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        <p><strong>Good news<% if (firstName) { %>, <%= firstName %><% } %>!</strong></p>
        <p>You're already on our mailing list.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="details">
        <p>You're all set to receive updates from Paper Street Thrift.</p>
        <p>Keep an eye on your inbox for our latest news and offers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="message" style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px;">
        <p>Thanks for being part of our community!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Paper Street Thrift</strong></p>
      <p>Quality secondhand goods with character</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
